description: This course is based on Brian Tracy's Book, "21 secrets of Self-made millionaires",which is translated, edited and customized according to Urdu/Hindi speaking students. The principles described in the course are powerful and can transform lives. Exercises at the end of each lecture will help students make actionable plan towards achieving financial goals.
title: Learning to be financially independent
instructors: Teaching is my passion! Muhammad Imran Sajid
